data.meta_description: Quantium 410 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The Quantium 410 is Tokheim's global multiproduct fuel dispenser with a 'hanging hose' design for easy access. It offers quality, reliability, and uptime based on data from over 40,000 service stations. Key features include hose retraction for convenient filling, payment options to increase retailing and security, and high-quality hydraulics for accurate dispensing. Technical specifications include speeds up to 130 l/min and options for integrated payment and customized designs.
